  "voice_observations": {
    "caption_text": "Coming to Rio with @hm reminded me what it means to simply be yourself.\nThere’s a freedom here, an openness that invites you to move, to create, to live without holding back. The city doesn’t wait for the right moment. It moves, and you move with it.\nWhat inspires me most isn’t just Rio’s beauty, but its honesty. The way people show up as they are: unfiltered, generous, alive.\nEvery encounter feels like a reminder: that being yourself isn’t something to find, it’s something to live.\nWhat began in New York continues here, with new light, new rhythm and the same belief.\nBe you. Always.\n/Rafael Pavarotti",
